   Eric Liu:
   Why ordinary people need to understand power
   TEDCity2.0 · 17:15 · Filmed Sep 2013
   Subtitles available in 2 languages
   View interactive transcript
   Share this idea Watch Later Download Rate Share on Twitter Share via
   Facebook Share by Email Embed this talk
